cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on improving the performance of image and video recognition models under adverse conditions using deep learning-based frameworks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also extensively uses deep neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with video recognition, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper proposes a transfer learning approach, which could also place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
